.SH Description
.PP
Functions \f[C]MPI_Graphdims_get\f[R] and \f[C]MPI_Graph_get\f[R]
retrieve the graph-topology information that was associated with a
communicator by \f[C]MPI_Graph_create\f[R].
.PP
